[smp-4core] core 0 selects thread A
[smp-4core] core 1 selects thread B
[smp-4core] core 2 selects thread C
[smp-4core] core 3 selects thread D
[smp-4core] determineTargetCore A = core 0
[smp-4core] determineTargetCore B = core 1
[smp-4core] determineTargetCore C = core 2
[smp-4core] determineTargetCore D = core 3
[smp-4core] wake D from core 0 emits SGI reschedule to core 3
[smp-4core] wake A from core 0 emits no SGI (local)
[smp-4core] switch core 1 to B sets current = thread B
[smp-4core] core 0 emptied with idle enqueued selects the idle thread
